node.text:
Can’t hide my excitement anymore! 
We just reached 400k. 
Thank you so much each one of you. 
Although the journey was not easy, you all made it possible.
We went through ups and downs in our lives but your constant support for this page means everything to me. 

You could have picked millions of people to follow… Good choice though.😜
Your constant comments, appreciation, likes, and sharing of my content are what made me so strong in the world of social media. Deeply overwhelmed with the response. Thank you for your immense love!

With love,
Vishal Ahuja.
